src.controller.delegator module¶

class src.controller.delegator.Delegator(view_main: src.view.view_main.ViewMain)¶

Bases: object

This class delegates the user interface components loaded in from the specified UI file by PyQt5’s uic library. It delegates them to static wrapper objects that will contain specific sets of those components and manage them accordingly.
